        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Founded in 2026, SmartNest Pet Tech emerged from a simple yet powerful question: <strong>"How can we use technology to improve the lives of pets and their owners?"</strong></p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Our founders, a team of pet lovers and tech enthusiasts, noticed that modern pet parents face unique challenges. Busy work schedules, frequent travel, and the desire to provide the best care for their furry friends created a need for innovative solutions.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Today, SmartNest serves thousands of happy customers worldwide with our comprehensive range of smart pet care products. From smart pet cameras to GPS trackers, automatic feeders to smart litter boxes, we're committed to making pet care easier, smarter, and more connected.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Headquartered in Shenzhen, China – the world's technology hub – we combine cutting-edge innovation with meticulous quality control to deliver products that exceed expectations.</p>
